      <title>戴利表示，除非有必要，否则美联储不应采取紧急降息行动</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-fed-should-not-act-urgently-when-its-not-required-daly-says-2024-04-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山联邦储备银行行长玛丽·戴利周一表示，美国“不急于”降息，因为经济和劳动力市场强劲，通胀率仍高于美联储 2% 的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-fed-should-not-act-urgently-when-its-not-required-daly-says-2024-04-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 00:54:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
